# Input

```yaml
- 'plain text'
- 'has ''single'' quotes'
- "has \"double\" quotes"
- '\n not an escape'
- "tab\tescape"
- "''"
- '""'

```


# Formatted

```yaml
- "plain text"
- "has 'single' quotes"
- 'has "double" quotes'
- '\n not an escape'
- "tab\tescape"
- "''"
- '""'

```
